name: Mariana Torres Torres
description: Hey, I'm Mariana! I'm a 5th year student at the University of Florida mayoring in Computer Science Engineering and minoring in Geography. I was born and raised in Caracas, Venezuela, but now I am based in Gainesville, Florida. When I'm not coding, I like to paint, embroider, play videogames, and hike. Fun Fact: one of my life goals is to visit all 63 US National Parks (6 so far!).
